{"tid":2493050,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(26) 電瓶車討論區 [玖拾陸]","createTime":"2021-04-17T14:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T17:18:25.000Z","uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d10101a93894a1e0dfe1ef9664d6709d3c4c4b5a","tid":2493050,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>置頂post未完成，請接龍 <img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdZGhmWkqL3kRomYwwkS1qjcD1TSE7vBvWD1ArBNinsXk?filename=oRnPm4t.gif&amp;h=49f06f33&amp;s=1080\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme4CjeuaiR8wZq5KDUwSt6fVuU5HxSHQ32aXjGNpPqEcz?filename=LbtnGNr.gif&amp;h=9822694d&amp;s=1080\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbLRiVHTwqTn6QYCW33FFbaH1Piiryo8VcBwVU1vbMRpS?filename=EDoOEVx.gif&amp;h=9d5a375c&amp;s=1080\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme74kRkpszHqi9q3ttrzxXcmZsZyhcVP8eFSscnvfqesA?filename=vfnWMDO.gif&amp;h=08b6b10b&amp;s=1080\" /><br />\n<br />\n***<br />\nQ: 想學電單車, 邊間好?<br />\nA: 關於學車問題, 請移玉步至隔離post 「考緊26？你問我答！」<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新牌買咩車好？<br />\nA: 請參考<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFszC8jutcs&amp;list=PLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVFszC8jutcs%26list%3DPLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N%26index%3D3&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=f45557bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFszC8jutcs&amp;list=PLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N&amp;index=3</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\nQ:邊到買車好?<br />\nA: 二手: 28car, facebook marketplace<br />\n新車視乎牌子: (紅色係總代理, 其他係分銷商, 以下為大路牌子)<br />\nHonda: <span class=\"red\">燦基 (旺角)</span>, 恆基 (銅鑼灣), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nYamaha: <span class=\"red\">萬里達 (太子)</span>, 銀星 (深水埗), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nKawasaki: <span class=\"red\">泰力 (北角)</span>, 翔利 (土瓜灣), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nSuzuki: 鈴木科研 (觀塘), 文偉 (堅尼地城)<br />\nDucati: Ducati Hong Kong (新蒲崗)<br />\nKTM: KTM Hong Kong (新蒲崗)<br />\nSYM (三陽): 奧士 (大角咀)<br />\nVespa: Motoplex (土瓜灣)<br />\n<br />\n水貨車: DS MOTO (大角咀)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 學車買咩頭盔好？<br />\nA: 睇$做人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大路鋪頭有<br />\n土瓜灣: 車迷 油麻地: 頭盔 元朗/深水埗: 預瘋  九龍城:熊興(Arai代理) 花墟:加利(Shoei代理) <br />\n<br />\nQ: 電單車(26)有咩種類?<br />\nA: 同46一樣, 有分棍波同自動波, 外型大致上可分為:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.supermoto8.net/images/article/37b81ae2acdba2bef1af4b5ccc1a04812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supermoto8.net%2Fimages%2Farticle%2F37b81ae2acdba2bef1af4b5ccc1a04812.jpg&h=acbac303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啡鈴(sport bike)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 模仿真實賽車的外型, 坐姿偏高, 騎姿會比較趴, 因為有流線型外殼(fairing)包裹故俗稱啡鈴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://motocity.tw/menu/Bike/honda/2014/cb400/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmotocity.tw%2Fmenu%2FBike%2Fhonda%2F2014%2Fcb400%2F01.jpg&h=e45b1710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n街車(naked bike)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主(亦有少量自動波款), 坐姿比啡鈴舒適, 適合於市區使用, 因為無外殼所以英文會叫naked bike<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://moto7.net/imgs/honda-rebel500-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoto7.net%2Fimgs%2Fhonda-rebel500-1.jpg&h=5c040cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巡航車(cruiser)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 特點係腳踏偏前, 坐姿舒適且坐高低, 適合長時間駕駛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/no/zeek__596/2d897972476611c9547ae042a2d9f6cc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2Fzeek__596%2F2d897972476611c9547ae042a2d9f6cc&h=718e8aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綿羊(scooter)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 自動波為主, 亦細分有龍骨同平地台(無龍骨), 坐姿舒適且靈活, 另外有大容量貯物空間, 適合於市區使用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.webike.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/010-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.webike.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F010-4.jpg&h=8cb37418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爬雞(dual-sport/off-road)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 車身輕而且坐高較高, 主力用於非鋪裝路面(爛路/越野）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"781b32cdf69dd188b82ad024461bffab0929049f","tid":2493050,"uid":117503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"玖拾陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d628cea851ca78958ebf2d5869c9f77da7d7be8","tid":2493050,"uid":101742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"新手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec02be45be4c39909c04dbe3887e3efaa9a924d","tid":2493050,"uid":101742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781b32cdf69dd188b82ad024461bffab0929049f","tid":2493050,"uid":117503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"玖拾陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"到壹佰使唔使攪啲嘢賀一賀佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0594695b9c9caf8ff97de9a1a6ea3d9f136add","tid":2493050,"uid":117503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eec02be45be4c39909c04dbe3887e3efaa9a924d","tid":2493050,"uid":101742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781b32cdf69dd188b82ad024461bffab0929049f","tid":2493050,"uid":117503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"玖拾陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:06